<subSubSection id="92D94B89F6B7404838B801AFCBC0E6A3" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="9CDC8016F1915BFC8E79DF47EC85A054" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<taxonomicName id="498BAF77422317CC909A5BB4F54A965D" authorityName="Steyskal" authorityYear="1980" class="Insecta" family="Phytomyzinae" genus="Haplopeodes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Haplopeodes" order="Diptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Haplopeodes</taxonomicName>
Steyskal, 1980: 141. Type species: 
<taxonomicName id="EF51E47705726EC841C61382D5DD3779" baseAuthorityName="Meigen" baseAuthorityYear="1838" class="Insecta" family="Phytomyzinae" genus="Phytomyza" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Phytomyza minuta" order="Diptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="minuta">Phytomyza minuta</taxonomicName>
<bibRefCitation id="9075F97F47DF7C1E8AC5ED8EA3445395" author="Frost, SW" journalOrPublisher="Memoir of the Cornell Agricultural Experiment Station" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="1 - 228" refId="B75" refString="Frost, SW, 1924. A study of the leaf-mining Diptera of North America. Memoir of the Cornell Agricultural Experiment Station 78: 1 - 228" title="A study of the leaf-mining Diptera of North America." volume="78" year="1924">Frost 1924</bibRefCitation>
